sentences: Megan Elizabeth McKenna (born 26 September 1992) is an English television personality and singer.

She went on to become a housemate in the seventeenth series of Celebrity Big Brother in 2016.
She was the fourth housemate to be evicted having received the fewest votes to save, spending a total of 18 days in the house.
